Edwardsburg clinches league title 
THREE RIVERS – Isaiah Miller rushed for 152 yards and scored five touchdowns as Edwardsburg overwhelmed Three Rivers 65-21 to remain unbeaten and clinch the outright Wolverine Conference football title.
